### Hadith 1:525

*Narrated Anas bin Malik:*

Allah's Apostle used to offer the 'Asr prayer at a time when the sun was
still hot and high and if a person went to Al-'Awali (a place) of
Medina, he would reach there when the sun was still high. Some of
Al-'Awali of Medina were about four miles or so from the town.

